Usage:

Firstly, prepare the environments(sysroot) using adb:
$ ./qmake_embedded.sh ~/sysroot
Creating ~/sysroot from adb...
...
~/sysroot/qmake (for aarch64-linux-gnu) is ready!

Or using rsync:
$ ./qmake_embedded.sh ~/sysroot 172.16.22.13
Creating ~/sysroot from 172.16.22.13...
...
~/sysroot/qmake (for aarch64-linux-gnu) is ready!

Then you can use the generated qmake wrapper for cross compiling.

For qtcreator, add it in Tools->Options->Kits->Qt Versions->Add.
